      <title>斯图纳拉斯告诉自由党，欧洲央行 2024 年更有可能实施三次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-stournaras-sees-more-likely-three-rate-cuts-in-2024-liberal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员雅尼斯·斯托纳拉斯表示，欧洲央行今年可能会三次降低借贷成本，而不是四次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ecb-stournaras-sees-more-likely-three-rate-cuts-in-2024-liberal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:41:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安进首席执行官公布实验性肥胖药物最新进展后股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amgen-soars-after-ceo-gives-update-on-experimental-obesity-drug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安进公司 (Amgen Inc.) 首席执行官表示，对该公司实验性肥胖药物 MariTide 的早期研究结果“非常鼓舞”，该公司股价在尾盘飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/amgen-soars-after-ceo-gives-update-on-experimental-obesity-drug</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
